initial_reviews.review_content:
What do you like best about User.com?
- this app helps in automatization and personalization of your marketing communication;
- I really like that I can have all in one place: I can send emails and text messages, I can have live chat, show pop-ups and push notifications on my website and create dynamic page content;
- they also have a great CRM system which helps me save precious time thanks to the possibility of the repetitive tasks;
- you can have full control over your teammates' performance thanks to reporting modules;
- and what is great is their support - they help to solve problems immediately.

What do you dislike about User.com?
Nothing to dislike at the moment, if something appears, I will get back to this review.

What problems is User.com solving and how is that benefiting you?
It's a real time-saver when you have all communication channels in one place

